description:
The second collaboration pack of "Touhou LostWord" songs have already arrived!
Once again, it features 6 songs from popular MV Projects!
Please enjoy this music pack full of songs just as popular as Vol. 1!

This pack contains the following:

■6 Songs
・The Moon and Izayoi / Touhou LostWord feat. nano × KISHIDA KYOUDAN & THE AKEBOSHI ROCKETS
・Blue Goodbyes / Touhou LostWord feat. Toshihiko Tahara × Butaotome
・Disillusion / Touhou LostWord feat. Faylan × Alstroemeria Records
・Night-Splitting Light / Touhou LostWord feat. Hironobu Kageyama × Butaotome
・Moonlit Festival! / Touhou LostWord feat. Eimi Naruse+Ringo Coisio from Band Ja Naimon MAXX NAKAYOSHI × IOSYS
・TataeLost / Touhou LostWord feat. Kishida Mel × Sekkenya

■6 Challenge Stages
・Lv.5 If Only (Disillusion)
・Lv.6 Game of Bubbles (TataeLost)
・Lv.7 Wasshoi, Wasshoi! (Moonlit Festival)
・Lv.8 How to Thunderswipe Bubble (Night-Splitting Light)
・Lv.9 Do You Have to Keep Asking? (Blue Goodbyes)
・Lv.10 Together on a Moonlit Night (The Moon and Izayoi)

* Internet connection required for purchase.
* Game must be restarted after songs are purchased in order to use them.
name: Touhou LostWord Song Pack Vol.2
